## High-Level App Structure
- **Authentication Flow**:
  - Login page with admin mockup credentials
  - Firebase authentication integration
  - Route protection for unauthenticated users

- **Main Dashboard**:
  - Real-time device monitoring
  - System performance charts (CPU, Memory)
  - Device list with filtering
  - Notification service for state changes

- **Device Detail Page**:
  - Comprehensive device information
  - Connection details
  - Associated entities list
  - Status indicators

## App Navigation
- **Home** (`/`) - Redirects to dashboard if authenticated, login if not
- **Login** (`/login`) - Authentication page with admin mockup
- **Dashboard** (`/dashboard`) - Main monitoring view with summary cards
- **Device Detail** (`/dashboard/device/[id]`) - Detailed device information

## Data Types
- **Device**: Hardware devices with properties like manufacturer, model, connections
- **Entity**: Components or services provided by devices
- **HomeAssistantSnapshot**: Time-based logs with system metrics